message: Tweeten 4.6.3 fixes some major installation-related issues:
new: UI fixes for Tweeten Blck, Dark, and Light.
Fixes an issue where users couldn't update from older versions (4.5.3 and older)
Fixes an issue where users couldn't update from 4.6.0 to newer versions
warning: If Tweeten fails to update for you and you are not runnning version 4.6.3, please update manually from the website here.
